description: Did you ever hear about a sport called "parkour"? Well, I have actually never heard about it - until yesterday. The guy I met close to a Metro station was checking out the area if it was suitable for him and his friends to train. Parkour is basically about jumping around and climbing walls. I don´t know how to describe it better with my limited English. However, this boy was very communicative and I asked him if he could show me a bit of this sport. He stated that he would like to... but that his jeans are too tight. Well, for a statement like this I am only waiting for. I offered him 2 000 to do it just in his undies. It was kinda sexy to see this young fellow being able to move like a monkey (sorry for the wording) just in his underwear. So I offered him more to follow me to a hotel room...
title: Czech Hunter 207
